<comment>
  I developed a WebApp to create little books.
</comment>

We can write comment in between frames.

<comment>
  And this is my report on "The Little Typer".
</comment>

<get_reader_input label="start">
  <comment>
    Would you like to start?
  </comment>
</get_reader_input>

<match>
  <case> Yes
    <comment>
      Ok let us start.
    </comment>
  </case>

  <case> No
    <comment>
      Really?
    </comment>
    <comment>
      Let us try again.
    </comment>
    <jump module="developer-s-note"></jump>
  </case>

  <default>
    <comment>
      Invalid answer, please try again.
    </comment>
    <jump label="start"></jump>
  </default>
</match>
